Title: Lucas County ARES Net Control Software
Description:
Lucas County ARES Net Control Software

This software was primarily developed to assist Amateur Radio Operators running Net Control stations.  Modeled after our local ARES Traffic and Skywarn Nets.

See documentation for features and benefits of this software.
